Minimum Requirements
--------------------
    * Python 2.7

Visualization Module Requirements
---------------------------------
    * Matplotlib 2.1.0 or higher.

Classification Module Requirements
----------------------------------
    * PyML 0.7.14 or higher.


Installation
------------
Download tarball and unpack:

    tar -xfz SpliceGrapher-0.2.7.tar.gz
    cd SpliceGrapher-0.2.7

You can carry out a standard installation.  If you wish to specify a
separate directory for the command-line scripts, you can do so using
the --install-scripts option.

For example, if the modules are installed in /mystuff/lib/python/SpliceGrapher-0.2.7
and you want the scripts in /usr/bin (e.g., /usr/bin/selectModel.py), then use:

    python setup.py install --home=/mystuff --install-scripts=/usr/bin

